Metadata.Title: Hokkaido Cable Car Simulator 2017
Metadata.Description: Have fun riding on the Hokkaido cable car all day with this exciting contract! No targets, infinite cable car fun! Just don't tell IOI you been getting free rides all day without any killing."Hokkaido Cable Car Simulator 2017 is the best game ever"-Spraystealer"The cable car fell out of the sky. I want a refund,"-Yuki Yamazaki"A contract to die for"-Agent 47
